results.name: Number of non-isomorphic multiset partitions of weight n with no constant parts.
comment: Also the number of nonnegative integer matrices up to row and column permutations with sum of elements equal to n and no zero rows or columns, in which every row has at least two nonzero entries.
The weight of a multiset partition is the sum of sizes of its parts. Weight is generally not the same as number of vertices.
